=========================
post request means
frondend(fe) le backend(be) laai get request baat pathauchh
tyo bela FE le  data banauchh eg name,age,address ect
tyo data laai BE ma request send garchh pos request ma data band gareer pathauchh
bE le validation check garer data correct bhaye table ma rakhchh
